        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Update router firmware to latest version</li>
        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Disable WPS (WiFi Protected Setup) - security vulnerability</li>
        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Use WPA3 or WPA2 encryption (not WEP or WPA)</li>
        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Create strong WiFi password (12+ characters)</li>
        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Disable remote management unless needed</li>
        <li class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed pl-2">‚úì Change default SSID (network name) to something unique</li>
